<br>

Skylight is free up to the first 100,000 requests. After that, 
pricing starts at $20 per million requests handled, and continues 
according to the schedule above. As you can also see, the more you 
need, the lower your cost per million; built-in bulk discounting.

To be clear: no plans, nothing to choose. Skylight will automatically 
discount additional requests for you. We're fond of simplicity.


